OL,3,CTV has long been inaccessible for
OL,4,Cdisabled people, says Adolescence
OL,5,Cwriter
OL,7,FLatest data shows disabled people make
OL,8,Fup 9.7% of the off-screen workforce
OL,9,Fcompared to the national workforce
OL,10,Faverage, which is 20%, as ITV News
OL,11,FArts Editor Nina Nannar reports
OL,13,FWhile disability representation on
OL,14,Fscreen in the TV and film industry is
OL,15,Fimproving, barriers for disabled
OL,16,Fpeople working behind the camera
OL,17,Fremain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
