OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779825947
OL,3,CTV has long been inaccessible for
OL,4,Cdisabled people, says Adolescence
OL,5,Cwriter
OL,7,FMulti-award-winning screenwriter Jack
OL,8,FThorne, whose credits include
OL,9,FAdolescence, Falling, Toxic Town and
OL,10,FHarry Potter and the Cursed Child, has
OL,11,Fspent years using his platform to
OL,12,Fimprove access for those working
OL,13,Fbehind the scenes.
OL,15,FThorne, who has cholinergic urticaria,
OL,16,Fa chronic skin condition, and was
OL,17,Fdiagnosed with autism as an adult, is
OL,18,Fpart of the TV Access Project, an
OL,19,Findustrywide initiative aiming to
OL,20,Fmake sets and productions more
OL,21,Faccessible and inclusive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779825947
OL,3,CTV has long been inaccessible for
OL,4,Cdisabled people, says Adolescence
OL,5,Cwriter
OL,7,FThe latest data from Creative
OL,8,FDiversity Network shows disabled
OL,9,Fpeople make up 9.7% of the off-screen
OL,10,Fworkforce compared to the national
OL,11,Fworkforce average, which is 20%.
OL,13,FAt the National Film and Television
OL,14,FSchool (NFTS) in Beaconsfield, a new
OL,15,Fpurposebuilt accommodation and study
OL,16,Fblock is under construction.
OL,18,FDesigned to be fully accessible, it
OL,19,Fwill enable disabled students to live
OL,20,Fand study on campus for the first time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779825947
OL,3,CTV has long been inaccessible for
OL,4,Cdisabled people, says Adolescence
OL,5,Cwriter
OL,7,FThe facility is intended to remove
OL,8,Fsome of the most fundamental barriers
OL,9,Fto entering the industry.
OL,11,FWith accessible accommodation and
OL,12,Flearning spaces built in from the
OL,13,Foutset, students will be able to train
OL,14,Fin studios designed around their needs.
OL,16,FThorne recently toured the site
OL,17,Falongside the NFTS's new Disability
OL,18,FLead, Hamish Thompson, describing
OL,19,Fprojects like this as essential if the
OL,20,Findustry is to change.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779825947
OL,3,CTV has long been inaccessible for
OL,4,Cdisabled people, says Adolescence
OL,5,Cwriter
OL,7,F"With disability, you've actually got
OL,8,Fto change the space, and the
OL,9,Fextraordinary thing that's happening
OL,10,Fhere is that they're prepared to
OL,11,Fchange the space," said Thorne.
OL,13,F"Disabled people can't work in spaces
OL,14,Fthat are inaccessible and TV has got
OL,15,Fby on being inaccessible for a very,
OL,16,Fvery long time."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
