CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779825947
OL,3,CTV has long been inaccessible for
OL,4,Cdisabled people, says Adolescence
OL,5,Cwriter
OL,7,FHe added: "When the TV access project
OL,8,Fwas first set up, there was one
OL,9,Faccessible toilet in the whole of the
OL,10,FUK for location filming. If you needed
OL,11,Fto use the loo and you're a disabled
OL,12,Fperson, you had to find a different
OL,13,Fway. You either had to drive to Tesco
OL,14,For Sainsbury's and use their toilets
OL,15,Fand drive back to set, or you had to
OL,16,Fcrawl across the floor."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
