OL,3,CTV has long been inaccessible for
OL,4,Cdisabled people, says Adolescence
OL,5,Cwriter
OL,7,FThorne acknowledges that his own entry
OL,8,Finto the industry, including writing
OL,9,Fon the Channel 4 series Skins, was
OL,10,Fsupported by opportunities that are
OL,11,Fstill not equally available to
OL,12,Feveryone.
OL,14,FBella Roberts, an editorial trainee
OL,15,Fand social media creator with more
OL,16,Fthan a million followers, has been
OL,17,Fdocumenting her experiences working in
OL,18,Ftelevision.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
