PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779825947
OL,3,CTV has long been inaccessible for
OL,4,Cdisabled people, says Adolescence
OL,5,Cwriter
OL,7,FThrough her content, she offers an
OL,8,Finsight into life behind the camera
OL,9,Fand the challenges of building a
OL,10,Fcareer with a disability.
OL,12,FRoberts, who lives with Hennekam
OL,13,FSyndrome, a rare genetic condition
OL,14,Fthat causes swelling and extreme
OL,15,Ffatigue, says getting employers to
OL,16,Funderstand her needs was difficult
OL,17,Fwhen she first started as a runner,
OL,18,Fsupporting production teams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779825947
OL,3,CTV has long been inaccessible for
OL,4,Cdisabled people, says Adolescence
OL,5,Cwriter
OL,7,FShe said: "I did loads of trial shifts
OL,8,Fwhen I began, and I could tell that
OL,9,Fwhen I left those shifts, I wasn't
OL,10,Fgetting the job.
OL,12,F"It's annoying because they couldn't
OL,13,Fsee my creative side, my editing side,
OL,14,Fthe things I had learned. They just
OL,15,Fsaw somebody who couldn't be on their
OL,16,Ffeet for 10 hours a day."
OL,18,FThe push for inclusivity comes at a
OL,19,Ftime when progress on screen is
OL,20,Fbecoming more visible.
