OL,3,CTV has long been inaccessible for
OL,4,Cdisabled people, says Adolescence
OL,5,Cwriter
OL,7,FIn television, the BAFTAwinning
OL,8,Fseries Code of Silence, starring deaf
OL,9,Factor Rose AylingEllis, has been
OL,10,Fwidely praised for putting disabled
OL,11,Ftalent at the centre of its
OL,12,Fstorytelling.
OL,14,FBut for many trying to break into the
OL,15,Findustry, the barriers remain
OL,16,Fsignificant, and removing them, Hamish
OL,17,Fsays, could transform not just who
OL,18,Fworks in television but the stories
OL,19,Faudiences see on screen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
