OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779825947
OL,3,CTV has long been inaccessible for
OL,4,Cdisabled people, says Adolescence
OL,5,Cwriter
OL,7,F"There's such a value in having these
OL,8,Fstories and they need to be told by
OL,9,Fdisabled people. That starts behind
OL,10,Fthe camera. In all cases," Hamish
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
